definitions.text:
@sổ toẹt
- (thông tục) Cross, reject
=Câu văn bị sổ toẹt+the sentence was crossed

@sổ lòng
- Just delivered
=Đứa con vừa mới sổ lòng+The baby has just been delivered

@sổng sểnh
- Unwatched, left unattended
=Để lồng gà sổng sểnh như thế thì sổ hết+If you leave the chicken cage inwatched like that, the fowl will all escape

@sổng
* verb
- to escape, to break loose

@sổ lồng
* verb
- to escape to break away, to be let out
